      • countBrute

        private static int countBrute​(java.util.List<java.lang.Character> string,
                              java.util.List<java.lang.Character> substring)
        Count occurrences of substring in string using the brute-force substring matching algorithm. Note findBrute is not used because it dose not find multiple occurrences of substring in each string. Therefore will be less efficient for substrings that occur multiple times within a word.
        Parameters:
        string - The string to search in.
        substring - The string to search for.
        Returns:
        The number of substring in string.
